                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7535" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-0763</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2681 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">初入江湖到扎根江湖：OPPO手机产品微创新模式发展之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">From entering the mobile phone Jianghu to taking root: the road to the development of the micro-innovation model of OPPO mobile phone products</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">胡京波，杨佩，刘芸（通讯作者），陈思成，吴琬桐 , 李冰如</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江西财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OPPO广东移动通信有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通讯业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">研发部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">产品微创新；微创新模式；模式实行机制；后发企业；OPPO手机；2023百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Product micro-innovation; Micro-innovation models; Model implementation mechanism; Latecomers; OPPO mobile phones</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着后发企业的快速崛起，越来越多的后发企业从追赶者转变为并跑者和领跑者。受限于资源、机会和技术，后发企业常在产品开发中选择微创新的方式。产品微创新是基于目前市场尚未挖掘的需求，重视在产品外观、功能和技术等方面进行改进，以产生新的产品特性或发掘出新的潜在用户。本案例描述了在手机江湖，身为后发企业的OPPO，2006年在模仿标杆企业设计的基础上对外观或功能进行创新，得以成功存活；2009年，OPPO失去模仿对象，通过局部技术突破满足用户需求，行业地位提升；2016年，三条产品线并进使资源分散导致业绩下降，通过整合核心需求实行“主系列一体化”，跃迁行业前列。因此，OPPO手机产品微创新模式类型及其特点是什么？其模式的实行机制是如何从“自上而下”标杆模仿转化为“自下而上”局部自主研制，最后怎样确定了主系列一体化的延续性？ </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the rapid rise of latecomers, more and more latecomers are moving from chasers to runners and leaders. Limited by resources, opportunities and technology, latecomers often opt for micro-innovation in product development. Product micro-innovation is based on untapped needs in the current market and focuses on improvements in product appearance, functionality and technology to generate new product features or uncover new potential users. This case describes how OPPO, a latecomer in the mobile phone industry, managed to survive in 2006 by imitating the designs of benchmark companies and innovating in terms of appearance or functionality. In 2016, OPPO&#39;s performance declined due to the fragmentation of resources caused by three product lines, and it leaped to the forefront of the industry by integrating its core needs and implementing &quot;main series integration&quot;. Therefore, what is the type of OPPO mobile phone product micro-innovation model and its characteristics? How did the implementation mechanism of the model change from &quot;top-down&quot; benchmarking to &quot;bottom-up&quot; local independent development, and how did it finally establish the continuity of the main series integration?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创新管理》、《产品创新与管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">产品微创新；产品微创新模式类型与特点；产品微创新模式的实行机制</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
